			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Repro steps:\r\n1. Start the game with a druid and level up (Ctrl-shift-L on the character)\r\n2. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n3. Debug Book\r\nGoto region > Act 1 > Forest > Abandoned Village\r\n4. Kill combat\r\n5. Head towards the windmill up the stairs.\r\n6. Morph into any wildshape.\r\n7. Talk to Fezzerk (Goblin with great axe)"
				},
